The word is out. We have added the historic 116-year-old The Bernards Inn to our collection of award-winning New Jersey restaurants. 

Since the announcement has reached the media, we have received numerous heartfelt and encouraging messages from families who had special events at the Bernards Inn and are excited for its restoration. Thank you everyone for reaching out with these stories, memories and wishes! 🙏 

I have a great respect for New Jersey’s historic businesses, and I get a kick out of infusing them with new vigor and fun ensuring they continue into the future. When I walk in The Bernards Inn I feel its greatness like an old stadium or theater. I think, wow, if these walls could talk.

This is one of New Jersey’s greatest, iconic properties. Our goal is to bring it back to its glory days. We’re looking forward to creating a must-go, top of its class and quintessential dining experience focused totally on the guest experience.

We look forward to a toast with you and your loved ones to all their cherished celebrations at the Bernards Inn soon!
